<div>
  <div class="background-index display-index">
    <div id="greeting-index"class="col-4 half-index">
      <div class="welcome-title-width-100">
       <h1 class="index-title">Welcome!</h1>
      </div>
      <br>
      <div class="welcome-title-width-100">
        <h2 style="color: #5B8E7D" class="title-highlight">How is your day going?</h2>
      </div>
      <br>
      <p>Let me know what's on your <span style="color: #d5875b">mind</span> and how you are <span style="color: #d5875b">feeling</span>. </p>
      <br>
      <p> <span style="color: #d5875b">First</span>, you can write down what's on your mind. </p>
      <br>
      <p> <span style="color: #d5875b">Then </span>, enter data for today - pains, moods, bleeding.</p>
        <br>
      <p>I will suggest you <span style="color: #d5875b">personalised</span> and tailor-made health advice for you today.</p>
      <br>
      <p>You can also <span style="color: #d5875b"> select </span> any calendar day in the past to see where you are in your <span style="color: #d5875b"> cycle</span>.</p>
      <div id="symptom-input">
      <%= render 'new' %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id= "calendar-index" class="col-5 row-3 half-index ">
      <%= render 'days/calendar' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="mascot"></div>
